quran[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Haa – Miim."
  43,2,"Mede Nwoma no a εda (biribiara) adi pefee no di nse sε:"
  43,3,"Nokorε, Yɛayε Qur’aan no wͻ Arab kasa mu sεdeε mobεte aseε."
  43,4,"Efiri Nwoma (nyinaa) Maame (Lawhul- Mah’fuuz) a εwͻ Yεnkyεn no mu, (Nwoma a) yɛamaso paa, adwen ne nyansa ahyε mma."
  43,5,"Enti Yɛnyi afutuo no mfiri mo so εnam sε moyε nnipa bͻnefoͻ nti?"
  43,6,"Nkͻmhyεfoͻ dodoͻ sεn na Yεsomaa wͻn baa tetefoͻ no hͻ?"
  43,7,"Nkͻmhyεni a ᴐbaa wᴐn hᴐ biara gyesε wͻdi ne ho fεw."
  43,8,"Yɛasεe wͻn a wͻyε den sen wͻn wͻ ahoͻden mu; na tetefoͻ no mfatoho adi wͻn anim kan atwam kͻ."
  43,9,"Sε wobisa wͻn nso sε: “Hwan na ͻbͻͻ soro ne asaase a? “Wͻbεka sε: “Otumfoͻ Onimdefoͻ no na Ɔbͻeε”."
  43,10,"(Otumfoͻ) no a, Wayε asaase de asε hͻ atrε mu ama mo, ayε akwan atoto mu sεdeε mobɛhunu kwan."
  43,11,"(Onyankopͻn) no a Ɔsane nsuo firi soro sεdeε εsε, na Yεde nyane asaase a awuo; saa ara na mo nso mobɛpue (afrii adakamena mu)."
  43,12,"(Otumfoͻ) no a Ɔbͻͻ biribiara mmienu mmienu, εna Wama mo nsuom hyεn ne nyεmmoa a moforo (tena wᴐn soᴐ),"
  43,13,"Sεdeε mobεtena wͻn akyi, na afei mobεkae Onyankopͻn adom wͻ εberε a mote so pintinn no na moaka sε: “Kronkron Hene ne Nea Wabrε wei ase ama yεn, na anka (yεn ara yεn mmͻdemmͻ mma) yɛntumi nnya."
  43,14,"Nokorε sε yɛ’Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ na yεbεsan akͻ."
  43,15,"Nanso wͻde kyεfa bi a εwͻ no ama Nenkoa no mu bi. Nokorε sε onipa yε boniayεni pefee."
  43,16,"Anaasε Onyankopͻn Ayi mmaa (ama Neho) wͻ deε Wabͻ no mu, εna Wayi mmarima ama mo?"
  43,17,"Nanso sε yεbͻ wͻn mu bi amaneε wͻ adeε a ͻdema Nyankopͻn no sεso (sε neyere awo ͻbaa) a na n’anim ayε kusuu (wamuna tumm), na nebo afu."
  43,18,"Anaasε deε yεde afεεfεdeε asiesie no a sε akyinnyeε ba a, ɔntumi nkasa nkyerεkyerε mu no (na mode no toto Onyankopͻn ho)?"
  43,19,"(Abosomsomfoͻ no) ayε Ahummͻborͻ Hene asomfoͻ Soro abͻfoͻ no nso mmaa. Wͻahunu (Soro abͻfoͻ no) bͻsuo (pεn a enti εma wͻkyerε sε soro abͻfoͻ yε mmaa)? Yεbεtwerε wͻn adanse-kunumu no, na yɛbɛbisa wͻn."
  43,20,"Deε wɔka ne sε: “Sε Ahummͻborͻ Hene no pε a anka yεnsom wͻn”. Wͻnni wei ho nimdeε, atorͻsεm na wͻdie."
  43,21,"Anaasε Yɛadi kan ama wͻn nwoma bi a wͻgyina soͻ?"
  43,22,"Daabi; Deε wͻka ne sε: “Yεbεtoo yεn agyanom wͻ (saa) kwan no so, na wͻn anammͻn so na εkyerε yεn kwan."
  43,23,"Saa ara na kͻkͻbͻni biara a Yɛdii kan somaa no dii w’anim kan wͻ kuro bi soͻ no, emu adefoͻ no kaa sε: “Nokorε sε yεbεtoo y’agyanom wͻ (saa) kwan (yi) so na wͻn anammͻn so na yεdi akyire."
  43,24,"(Kͻkͻbͻni no) kaa sε: “Na sε mede deε εtene kyεn deε mobεtoo no mo agyanom hͻ no brε mo mpo a?“ Wͻbuaa sε: “Yεdeε yεnnye deε yεde asoma mo no nni “."
  43,25,"Enti Yɛtuaa wͻn so ka; na hwε sεdeε wͻn a wͻannye (Nokorε no) annie no awieeε si wieeε."
  43,26,"Kae εberε a Abraham ka kyerεε n’agya ne nenkorͻfoͻ no sε: ”Medeε matwe me ho afiri deε mosom no ho."
  43,27,"Gyesε Nea Ɔbͻͻ me, efirisε Ɔno na Ɔbεkyerε me kwan."
  43,28,"Ɔyεε (saa kasa) no nsɛnnahɔ demaa nenkyiri mma sεdeε wͻbεsan (akͻ mu)."
  43,29,"Aane, Memaa saa nkorͻfoͻ no ne wͻn agyanom gyee wͻn ani kͻpem sε Nokorε no ne Ɔsomafoͻ a ͻda (nsεm no) adi pefee no baa wͻn hͻ."
  43,30,"Ɛberε a Nokorε no baeε no wͻkaa sε : “Wei deε εyε nkonyaa anaa naadaasεm, na yεn deε yεnye nni“."
  43,31,"Deε wͻka ne sε: “Adεn nti na yɛansane saa Qur’aan yi amma onipa a odi mu wͻ nkuro mmienu no mu (Maka ne Taif)?"
  43,32,"Wͻn na wͻkyekyε wo Wura Nyankopͻn Ahummͻborͻ no? Yεn na Yεkyekyε wͻn wiase asetena mu akͻnhoma no mu ma wͻn, εna Yεpagya ebinom kyεn ebinom wͻ gyinaberε mu sεdeε ebinom bεfa ebinom ama wᴐn ayε adwuma ama wᴐn. Na wo Wura Nyankopͻn ahummͻborͻ no yε kyεn (wiase ahonyadeε a) wͻreboaboa ano no."
  43,33,"Sε εnyε sε anhwε a nnipa nyinaa abεyε nnipa korͻ (anaasε wͻn nyinaa adwen bεtwe akosi wiase afεεfεdeε so) a, anka Yεbεma wͻn a wͻyi Ahummͻborͻ Hene no boniayε no afie nkurusoͻ ayε dwetε, na n’atwedeε a yεde forͻ no nso (ayε dwetε saa ara),"
  43,34,"Ne wͻn afie apono ne wͻn mpa a wͻdeda soͻ nso (ayε dwetε)-"
  43,35,"Ne sika kͻkͻͻ. Wei nom nyinaa yε wiase asetena mu anigyedeε, na Daakye no deε, εwͻ wo Wura Nyankopͻn hͻ dema Nyame-surofoͻ no (nko ara)."
  43,36,"Obi a ͻtwe ne ho firi Ahummͻborͻ hene no nkaekaeε ho no, Yεde no ma ͻbonsam ma ͻfa no yͻnkoͻ."
  43,37,"Nokorε sε, (abonsamfoͻ no) si wͻn kwan, na wͻn adwen yε wͻn sε wͻanya kwankyerε"
  43,38,"(Ɔbεkͻso saa ara) akosi sε ͻbεba Yεn hͻ, (saa berε no na) ͻbεka sε: ”Mɛnya a anka me ne wo (nipa bͻneni no) ntam kwan aware sεdeε apueε ne atͻeε (ntam tenten siteε); enti ͻyͻnko bͻne paa ne no."
  43,39,"Moyεε bͻne yi deε, ԑnnԑ da yi nokorε sε, kyε a mobεkyε asotwee no mu no ho mma mfasoͻ mma mo."
  43,40,"(Nkͻmhyεni), wobɛtumi ama ͻsosifoͻ ate asεm, anaa watene onifrani a ͻwͻ yera mu kͻ akyirikyi paa no?"
  43,41,"Enti sε Yɛyi wo firi hͻ mpo a, nokorε sε Yεbɛtua wͻn bͻne no so ka."
  43,42,"Anaa nso sε Yεbεma wo (atena ase) ahu deε Yɛahyε wͻn ho bͻ no; na εyε nokorε sε Yεwͻ wͻn so tumi."
  43,43,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), sͻ Adiyisεm a Yɛayi ama woͻ no mu yie; nokorε sε, wo wͻ kwan tenenee so."
  43,44,"Nokorε sε (Qur’aan yi) yε afutusεm ma wo ne wo nkorͻfoͻ, na yεbɛbisa mo (εho asεm)."
  43,45,"Bisa Asomafoᴐ no a Yԑsomaa wᴐn maa wᴐdii w’anim kan no sε: “Yɛfirii Mmͻborͻhunufoͻ Hene no akyi yεε anyame bi maa wͻn sε wͻnsom wͻn anaa?"
  43,46,"Nokorε sε Yεde Yεn nsεnkyerεnee somaa Mose maa no kͻͻ Farao ne nenhemfo hͻ, na ͻka kyerεε wͻn sε: “Meyε abͻdeε nyinaa Wura Nyankopͻn no Somafoͻ”."
  43,47,"Nanso εberε a ͻde Yεn nsεnkyerεnee no brεε wͻn no, hwε! wͻseree (Yεn nsεnkyeεnee no)."
  43,48,"Nsεnkyerεnee a Yɛyi kyerεε wͻn (akyire yi) biara no, na εso kyεn ne nua (nsεnkyerεnee dada a edii kan no); na Yεde asotwee sͻͻ wͻn mu sεdeε wͻbεsan wͻn akyi (afiri kwan bͻne so aba kwan pa no soͻ)."
  43,49,"Asεm a wͻka kyerεε (Mose) ne sε: “Nkonyaayini, frε wo Wura Nyankopͻn ma yεn sεdeε Ɔne wo bͻhyε kyerε no. Nokorε sε yεbεfa tenenee (kwan no) so."
  43,50,"Nanso εberε a Yɛyii asotwee no firii wͻn soͻ no, hwε! wͻbuu bͻhyε no so."
  43,51,"Farao bͻͻ no dawuro wͻ nenkorͻfoͻ no mu, ͻkaa sε: “Ɛnyε me na Misirim ahennie no ne saa nsubͻnten a εnenam m’ase yi wͻ me? Enti monhunu anaa?”"
  43,52,"Menyε nkyεn (Mose) wei, animguaseε (nipa) yi a ɔntumi nkasa pefee yi?"
  43,53,"Adεn na yεmma no sika kͻkͻͻ nkapo, anaasε Soro abͻfoͻ mma mmεka ne ho ne no nto santen?"
  43,54,"(Farao) yε maa ne nkorͻfoͻ no faa (asεm kεseε) no agodisεm, enti wͻyεε sotie maa no. Nokorε sε na wͻyε nkorͻfoͻ a wͻyε nsεmͻnedifoͻ paa."
  43,55,"Ɛberε a wͻhyεε Yεn abufuo no Yɛtuaa wͻn bͻne no so ka, na Yεmaa nsuo faa wͻn nyinaa."
  43,56,"Na Yεyεε wͻn nsεnnahͻ ne mfatoho de maa nkyiri mma no."
  43,57,"Ɛberε a yεbͻͻ Mar’yam ba (Yesu) din yεε mfatoho no, hwε sε na wo nkorͻfoͻ no de anigyeε reyε dede."
  43,58,"Wͻkaa sε: “Y’abosom no mmom na εyε anaa sε ͻno (Yesu)? Ɛnyε hwee ho nti na wͻyԑԑ saa mfatoho yi kyerԑԑ woᴐ, na mmom akyinnyeε nti. Aane, wͻyε nkorͻfoͻ bi a wͻyε akyinnyegyefoͻ paa."
  43,59,"(Yesu) gyinaberε ara ne sε ͻyε (Onyankopͻn) akoa a Yεde Y’adom dom no na Yεde no yεε mfatoho maa Israel mma."
  43,60,"Sε Yεpε a nka Yεbεma mo mu bi ayԑ Soro abͻfoͻ asi moanan mu wͻ asaase so."
  43,61,"Nokorԑ sԑ ͻno anaa ԑno ne dɔnhwere no nimdeε ho nsεnkyerεnee, enti monhwε na moamma moadwen annyε mo ntanta wͻ ho na monni m’akyi. Wei ne ͻkwan tenenee no."
  43,62,"Na momma ͻbonsam nsi mo kwan; nokorε sε ͻyε motamfo pefee."
  43,63,"Ԑberε a Yesu de nyinasoͻ ne nkyerεkyerεmu pefee baeε no ͻkaa sε: “Nokorε mede adwen (anaasε nyansa) abrε mo, na merebεkyerε mo nneεma bi a monte moho ase wͻ ho no ho. Enti monsuro Nyankopͻn na monyε sotie mma me “."
  43,64,"Nokorε sε Onyankopͻn na Ɔyε me Wura εna Ɔyε monso mo Wura, enti monsom no. Wei ne ͻkwan tenenee no."
  43,65,"Nanso wͻn mu mmusua kuo no mu kyekyɛɛeɛ. Enti due nka wͻn a wͻyε bͻne no wͻ asotwee yaaya da no."
  43,66,"Enti deε wͻretwεn ara ne sε Dͻnhwere no bεba wͻn so mpofirim wͻ abrε a wͻnnim?"
  43,67,"Saa Da no ayͻnkofoͻ bεdane atamfoͻ ama wͻn ho wͻn ho, gyesε Nyamesurofoͻ no."
  43,68,"(Yεbεka akyerε agyidiefoͻ no sε): “Menkoa, suro biara nnihͻ dema mo Ɛnnε da yi, na mowerε nso nho."
  43,69,"(Menkoa no a) na wͻgye Yεn Nsεm no die a na wͻyε Muslimifoͻ, brε wɔn ho aseε no."
  43,70,"“Mone moyerenom monfa anigyeε nwura Soro aheman no mu."
  43,71,"Sika nyowa ne nkuruwa bɛtwa wͻn ho ahyia; ͻkra akͻnnͻdeε ne deε εyε anii fε biara bi wͻ mu; na emu na mobεtena afe bͻͻ."
  43,72,"Wei ne Soro aheman no a εnam dwumadie a modiiε no ho nti yεbεma mo adi adeε wͻ mu no."
  43,73,"Mowͻ nnuaba pii wᴐ mu, na emu na mobɛdidie."
  43,74,"Nokorε sε abͻneεfoͻ no bεtena Amanehunu gya asotwee mu."
  43,75,"Yεngo (asotwee no) mu mma wͻn koraa, na emu na wͻbɛnya abamu buo."
  43,76,"Ɛnyε Yεn na Yɛdii wͻn amim, na mmom na wͻyε abͻneεfoͻ."
  43,77,"Wͻbɛsu (afrε ͻbͻfoͻ a ͻhwε Egya no soͻ no sε): “Maalik, Mawo Wura Nyankopͻn nku yεn prεko.” (Maalik) bεka akyerε wͻn sε: “Mobεtena mu afe bͻͻ."
  43,78,"Ampa sε Yεde Nokorε no abrε mo, nanso mo mu pii kyiri Nokorε no."
  43,79,"Anaasε (Qurashfoͻ), moabͻ (Me Nkͻmhyεni no ho) pͻ bͻne bi anaa? Ɛneε Yεn nso Yɛafa adwen."
  43,80,"Anaasε (abͻneεfoͻ no) dwen sε Yεnte wͻn nsumaeε mu ne wͻn kokoa mu agyinatuo no mu nsεm anaa? Daabi, Y’asomafoͻ wͻ wͻn hͻ a wͻretwerε (biribiara)."
  43,81,"(Nkͻmhyεni), ka sε: ”Sε Ahummͻborͻ Hene no wͻ ba a, εneε me ne asomfoͻ no nea odi kan”."
  43,82,"Kronkron Hene ne ͻsoro ne asaase Wura Nyankopͻn, Tumi Ahennwa Wura no Ɔkorͻn, so kyεn deε wͻde susu no no."
  43,83,"Enti (Nkͻmhyεni), wodeε gyae wͻn ma wͻnkeka nsεm hunu na wͻnni agorɔ nkosi sε wͻbɛhyia wͻn Da no a yɛahyε wͻn ho bͻ no."
  43,84,"Ɔno ne Nyankopͻn wͻ soro, na Ɔno ara nso ne Nyankopͻn wͻ asaase so, na Ɔne Onyansafoͻ no, na Ɔno ara nso ne Onimdefoͻ no a Ɔnim biribiara no."
  43,85,"Nhyira ne Nea ͻsoro ne asaase so, ne deε εwͻ mfimfii (nyinaa) ahennie wͻ no no, na Ne hͻ na Dͻnhwere no ho nimdeε no wͻ; na Ne hͻ na mobεsan akͻ."
  43,86,"Wͻn a wͻfiri N’akyi su frε wͻn no nni ntwitwagyeε ho tumi, na mmom gyesε wͻn a wͻdi Nokorε no ho adanseε no, na wͻnim (sɛ Nyankopɔn yɛ baako ampa)."
  43,87,"Sε wobisa wͻn sε: “Hwan na Ɔbͻͻ wͻn a, wͻbεka sε: “Nyankopͻn”. Adεn na afei wͻretwe wͻn ho (firi Nokorε no ho)?"
  43,88,"(Nkͻmhyεni) suu nesε: “Me Wura Nyankopͻn, weinom yε nkorͻfoͻ a wͻnnye nnie;"
  43,89,"(Nkͻmhyεni), Dane woho firi wͻn ho na ka sε: “Asomdwoeɛ.” Na εnkyε wͻbɛhu (nokorɛ a ɛwɔ mu biara)."
